And for if you are very security-oriented, there's the air-gapped Polkadot Vault (https://signer.parity.io/#about), which you can run on an old Android phone or iPhone. 

Since your tokens exist on-chain and wallets are just interfaces to interact with them, feel free to try a few and see what you like best!

Remember to be very careful with your sensitive account information!

LEDGER DOES NOT SUPPORT BITTENSOR (as you know)

Also, beware of people DMing you (there are people who will impersonate mods/admins/Foundation developers, but we will never DM you first).
